The Victoria Bridge will be lit Pink, Green, White, Light Blue, Yellow and Orange to celebrate FIFA Women&#39;s World Cup&nbsp;- Grand Final.

The 2023 FIFA Women&rsquo;s World Cup has been co-hosted across venues in Aotearoa/New Zealand and Australia and now it&rsquo;s time for the Grand Final!&nbsp;

Head to the Fan Festival&trade; at South Bank Parklands, to watch the Match live as well as enjoying an exciting program of music, entertainment, food and games.&nbsp;

Find out more at <a href="https://www.fifa.com/fifaplus/en/tournaments/womens/womensworldcup/australia-new-zealand2023" target="_blank">FIFA Women&rsquo;s World Cup Australia &amp; New Zealand 2023</a>&trade;.

This Light Up is organised by: Brisbane Economic Development Agency

